channel.title: Custom Items / Models make char invisible
channel.description:
I added models to the models folder, added their int's to the class8.java file, edited them on items.java on source side. But certain combinations of items equipped (such as.... Beautiful Cape, Armadyl Kiteshield and Barrows boots) make the character invisible.
Anyone have any ideas?
I'm sure it's a quick fix or something I missed.
